<b>That's not a bad idea.</b>

12:23.451 --> 12:26.751
<b>I didn't care about you guys at all
from the beginning.</b>

12:37.471 --> 12:38.931
<b>But...</b>

12:38.971 --> 12:43.521
<b>...my precious subordinates...</b>

12:43.561 --> 12:46.561
