is actually inside of my body...</b>

14:23.661 --> 14:24.371
<b>Hey!</b>

14:24.531 --> 14:26.331
<b>Don't panic!</b>

14:31.751 --> 14:34.841
<b>No matter how strongly we're attacked...</b>

14:35.961 --> 14:39.671
<b>Whether the Big Father leans or falls over...</b>

14:40.721 --> 14:44.011
<b>I'm the only one who'll get hurt.</b>

14:44.351 --> 14:48.731
<b>As long as you guys stay here,
you're not gonna get affected!</b>

14:48.891 --> 14:53.151
<b>--Come to think of it...
--It's only Bege-<i>san</i> who is suffering.</b>

14:55.061 --> 14:57.731
<b>We can hear Big Mom's voice...</b>

15:00.111 --> 15:02.451
<b>But it remains calm inside.</b>

15:06.121 --> 15:07.991
<b>That's right...</b>

15:08.041 --> 15:12.921
