even if I turn back to my human form.</b>

15:13.211 --> 15:16.631
<b>So you mean,
we'll be safe as long as we stay here...</b>

15:17.461 --> 15:22.341
<b>Listen... I'll change back to my human form
keeping you guys inside.</b>

15:22.381 --> 15:26.931
