15:38.611 --> 15:43.911
<b>We'll get riddled with bullets in an instant!
There's no chance of success!</b>

15:43.951 --> 15:46.281
<b>There are many users of the Color of Arms too!</b>

15:46.321 --> 15:48.791
<b>I can turn into gas but it doesn't matter!</b>

15:48.951 --> 15:51.411
<b>You don't know if there's any chance of success!</b>

15:51.581 --> 15:53.621
<b>You can't tell unless you try.</b>

15:53.791 --> 15:56.131
<b>You're only agile when you're escaping!</b>

15:56.291 --> 15:58.631
<b>What did you say, you fools?!</b>

15:58.801 --> 16:00.841
<b>Let me ask you a question.</b>

16:02.591 --> 16:03.551
<b>Sanji...</b>

16:06.591 --> 16:08.641
<b>Why did you save us?</b>

16:10.431 --> 16:15.271
