and we totally fell into the trap!</b>

16:22.441 --> 16:25.821
<b>Because my <i>father</i> would be sad...</b>

16:27.321 --> 16:30.871
<b>If I had stuck to my resentment
from my old days...</b>

16:34.001 --> 16:35.621
<b>Please let me out!</b>

16:35.671 --> 16:38.381
<b>Dad! I'm sorry!</b>

16:39.791 --> 16:43.591
<b>I'm sorry to be born weak!</b>

16:43.631 --> 16:45.971
<b>Help me, Dad!</b>

16:46.131 --> 16:49.641
<b>Help me! Dad!</b>

16:53.061 --> 16:56.641
<b>He'd be disappointed in me
for becoming such a small-minded rat...</b>

16:56.691 --> 17:00.571
<b>...who'd laugh at your blood family's death.</b>

17:01.271 --> 17:04.691
<b>Don't catch cold.</b>

17:05.491 --> 17:09.071
<b>I don't wanna live a life in which I'm too ashamed...</b>

17:09.121 --> 17:10.831
<b>...to face him!</b>

17:17.581 --> 17:21.091
<b>Don't ever admit that I'm your father...</b>

17:21.841 --> 17:25.721
<b>...in front of other people!</b>

17:30.341 --> 17:33.811
<b>It's a shame that I don't want anyone to know!</b>

17:34.771 --> 17:37.231
<b>You realize that, don't you?</b>

17:40.271 --> 17:42.111
<b>13 years ago,</b>

17:42.151 --> 17:46.651
<b>Vinsmoke Sanji who escaped from Germa
died once at sea...</b>

17:47.451 --> 17:49.991
<b>And that's what you wished for.</b>

18:02.131 --> 18:03.921
<b>So admit this!</b>

18:05.091 --> 18:09.301
<b>You're not my father, Vinsmoke Judge!</b>

18:10.261 --> 18:13.101
<b>Don't ever show yourself in front of us again!</b>

18:37.701 --> 18:39.371
<b>Very well.</b>

18:40.081 --> 18:41.711
<b>I promise...</b>

18:42.211 --> 18:43.961
<b>...I won't approach you...</b>

18:44.251 --> 18:47.341
<b>...or the East Blue!</b>

18:59.271 --> 19:01.771
<b>I already did my part!</b>

19:01.811 --> 19:04.441
<b>Doing more isn't part of our deal!</b>

19:09.491 --> 19:12.071
<b>Come out!</b>

19:12.491 --> 19:16.121
<b>Bege! Straw Hat!</b>

19:17.701 --> 19:19.751
<b><i>Come out!</i></b>

19:19.911 --> 19:21.501
<b>--Honey!
--Father!</b>

19:22.291 --> 19:26.001
<b>I don't wanna be here anymore!</b>

19:28.841 --> 19:32.971
<b>If nothing is done, you'll die too, Caesar!</b>

19:35.181 --> 19:36.851
<b>Open the gate!</b>

19:38.811 --> 19:43.271
<b>Gang Bege!
Until you and Caesar Clown fly away into the sky,</b>

19:43.311 --> 19:45.771
<b>we Germa will escort you!</b>

19:45.941 --> 19:47.401
<b>W-Wait a minute!</b>

19:47.441 --> 19:53.491
<b>Why do you decide what I'm gonna do?!
Your high-handed attitude hasn't changed, Judge!</b>

19:56.531 --> 20:00.081
<b>Oh, yeah... You Germa people can fly too...</b>

20:00.121 --> 20:02.201
<b>Then, we'll leave you behind, okay?</b>

20:02.371 --> 20:03.371
<b>No problem.</b>

20:05.921 --> 20:08.671
<b>Alright, if we need to buy time, I'll...</b>

20:09.881 --> 20:12.341
<b>--That's okay, Luffy.
--But...</b>

20:34.651 --> 20:38.411
<b>I don't wanna be indebted to this "failure"!</b>

20:41.201 --> 20:43.871
<b>That's how they wanna settle it...</b>

20:45.501 --> 20:47.331
<b>Wait, wait! Whoa-whoa!</b>

20:47.381 --> 20:50.541
<b>I didn't say I was gonna do this, you fools!</b>

20:50.751 --> 20:52.251
<b>Caesar!</b>

20:52.801 --> 20:54.221
<b>Shut up and do it!</b>

20:54.381 --> 20:56.881
<b>Ouch!</b>

20:56.931 --> 20:58.931
<b>You'll regret this!</b>

21:02.471 --> 21:05.691
<b>Come on out already!</b>

21:05.731 --> 21:07.271
<b>Bege!</b>

21:07.561 --> 21:10.191
<b>Straw Hat!</b>

21:13.691 --> 21:15.741
<b>Are you ready?</b>

21:16.241 --> 21:17.951
<b>Caesar Clown...</b>

21:18.111 --> 21:22.281
<b>I wasn't ready at all from the beginning!
You guys should protect me!</b>

21:22.451 --> 21:24.751
<b>Alright! Let's go crazy!</b>

21:26.411 --> 21:28.041
<b>You have the wrong idea.</b>

21:28.081 --> 21:33.131
<b>Our mission is to let Caesar and Bege escape
quickly and safely.</b>

21:33.551 --> 21:37.971
<b>This is a battle for evacuation.
Defense is harder than offense.</b>

21:38.131 --> 21:39.551
<b>I know.</b>

21:39.721 --> 21:41.551
<b>I understand the mission.</b>

22:00.161 --> 22:02.071
<b>Get ready to step out!</b>

22:02.281 --> 22:04.491
<b>Getting ready to step out!</b>

22:04.661 --> 22:07.331
<b>We're ready!</b>

22:07.871 --> 22:09.081
<b>Bege!</b>

22:12.131 --> 22:13.381
<b>All right!</b>

22:18.761 --> 22:21.591
<b>I'm gonna deactivate the castle!</b>

22:37.191 --> 22:38.281
<b>Let's go!</b>

22:56.461 --> 22:59.471
<b>Germa! Start attacking!</b>

23:09.431 --> 23:16.021
<b><i>Luffy and Germa 66 join forces
and a deadly escape plan begins!</i></b>

23:16.071 --> 23:20.281
<b><i>Big Mom's furious attacks raise Luffy's fighting spirit!</i></b>

23:20.321 --> 23:25.741
<b><i>To prove himself as the future King of the Pirates,
his special Gear Four techniques blast!</i></b>

23:25.911 --> 23:30.251
<b>On the next episode of One Piece!
"Escape From the Tea Party! Luffy vs. Big Mom!"</b>

23:30.291 --> 23:33.371
<b>I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!</b>
